425
00:40:33,900 --> 00:40:37,710
Neither the empress nor the crown prince are from the Gao family.

426
00:40:37,710 --> 00:40:40,530
It is inevitable that they will be disloyal.

427
00:40:40,530 --> 00:40:42,940
I'm not scared of the empress.

428
00:40:42,940 --> 00:40:45,870
She's just a female without a royal child.

429
00:40:45,870 --> 00:40:50,530
In the end, she has to rely on us. But the crown prince...

430
00:40:54,300 --> 00:40:56,840
I can't see through the crown prince.

431
00:40:57,840 --> 00:41:00,740
I have a feeling that once he is full-fledged,

432
00:41:00,740 --> 00:41:03,840
