433
00:41:05,470 --> 00:41:09,540
That's why I took this unwise move and made Ruyi enter the palace.

434
00:41:10,530 --> 00:41:13,610
Ruyi has always been intelligent since she was young.

435
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:16,420
If she can seize this opportunity

436
00:41:16,420 --> 00:41:19,890
