00:41:27,950 --> 00:41:32,760
About Ruyi serving in the His Imperial Majesty's bedchamber, have you asked the empress to make the arrangements?

439
00:41:33,390 --> 00:41:37,030
The empress specifically wanted me to tell you

440
00:41:37,030 --> 00:41:40,210
